<h2>Itching or burning, Mouth sores and White patches on tongue</h2>
<p>WebMD Symptom Checker helps you find the most common medical conditions indicated by the symptoms itching or burning, mouth sores and white patches on tongue including Seborrheic dermatitis, Allergic reaction, and Contact dermatitis.</p>
